## 🎥 Lesson 2.2 – DeSci & Blockchain for Science

[![Watch the video on YouTube](https://img.youtube.com/vi/RHBaPXsbOzs/0.jpg)](https://youtu.be/RHBaPXsbOzs)

### 🔍 Topics covered:
- **2.2.1 DeSci’s Mission & Objectives**:  
  Decentralizing science using blockchain.

- **2.2.2 Addressing Challenges in Science**:  
  • Transparency in funding  
  • Trustless collaboration through smart contracts  
  • Data traceability and verification tokens  
  • DAO organizations for research governance
